    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Rail Vikas Nigam Advisory Limited. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Distribution Manager to strengthen our Pune-based team.\n\nAbout Rail Vikas Nigam Advisory Limited:\nRail Vikas Nigam Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Flexible working hours\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Rail Vikas Nigam Advisory Limited!",
